00:18:52.220 --> 00:18:54.260
that will start your project.

00:18:55.640 --> 00:18:59.500
But on Heroku, which is a competitor of Railway,

00:18:59.560 --> 00:19:07.800
You can start both the web app and the worker in the same file.

00:19:08.920 --> 00:19:11.360
But you can't do that on Railway.

00:19:11.440 --> 00:19:13.480
