00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:31.060
They had a way to create a custom JSON for me,

00:19:33.360 --> 00:19:36.820
which managed to start both the web app

00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:40.560
and the worker in the same deployment.

00:19:41.320 --> 00:19:44.140
But I had to fight, to be honest with you,

00:19:44.300 --> 00:19:46.620
for like four or five hours to find a solution.

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:49.240
Because sometimes the problem,

00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:51.500
and that's the issue that I've seen a lot,

00:19:51.650 --> 00:19:55.300
is that traditional developers,

00:19:55.840 --> 00:19:59.200
professional developers, not people like me, not random guys like me,

00:19:59.820 --> 00:20:04.560
usually they assume that the people that they're supposed to explain things to

